Use mapper functions instead of strings in order to manually retrieve store values.
The function receives the store state and the component props.

@connect([{
     store: MyStore,
     props: (state, props) => {
         return {
             item: state.get('items').filter(item => item.get('id') === props.id)
         }
     }
